        "description": "Beam diameter 100-500 μm; smaller (100-200 μm) for fine surface preparation on slate, larger (300-500 μm) for broad area cleaning. 200 μm recommended for uniform contaminant removal on textured slate surfaces. Source: Equipment specifications from Coherent Inc. (Arma series) and industry case studies."
